reviewText: Very fast and easy to deal with.  Would buy from again.  Thank you
THIS VIDEO IS JUST WHAT I NEEDED TO LEARN FREE MOTION QUILTING.  THE INSTRUCTIONS WERE KEPT NICE AND SIMPLE.  I WOULD RECOMMEND TO EVERYBODY!!!!!

I am a beginning quilter and purchased all of Patsy's Fast & Free DVDs.  I am so glad I did!  She is a wonderful instructor who demonstrates and explains each technique very clearly.  I am no longer limited to my usual loop-d-doos!
